# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Kinyoubi Atelier & Co. — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# All variables are optional — features degrade gracefully.

# ─── Analytics (Umami) ───
# Sign up at https://cloud.umami.is or self-host
# NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_URL=https://cloud.umami.is

# ─── Live Chat (Crisp) ───
# Sign up at https://crisp.chat — free for 1 operator
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CRISP_WEBSITE_ID=

# ─── Scheduling (Cal.com) ───
# Sign up at https://cal.com — free tier, unlimited bookings
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CAL_USERNAME=

# ─── Contact Form Backend ───
# Option 1: Formspree (https://formspree.io) — 50 submissions/month free
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=

# Option 2: Web3Forms (https://web3forms.com) — 250 submissions/month free
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
